OL,4,CMan's family 'begged' for hospital
OL,5,Cvisit before he died
OL,6, A woman has described how she "begged"
OL,7, in vain to see her husband before he
OL,8, died in hospital.
OL,10,FDavid Howells, 57, spent two weeks on
OL,11,Fwards at Nottingham City Hospital after
OL,12,Fbeing admitted with complications
OL,13,Frelating to a heart condition.
OL,15,FExemptions to Covid restrictions allow
OL,16,Ffor some compassionate visits, but Mr
OL,17,FHowells' wife Sharon and daughter Kim's
OL,18,Frequests were refused.
OL,20,FThe hospital trust said it believed its
OL,21,Fpolicies were applied correctly.
